timeline.body: I might also add a test for a version like `1.24.0rc1-git2481dab2-md59a1c1708` as well, since we see that in our internal pants repo. timeline.body: Is there a reason we're using `Pattern.MULTILINE` here? I believe that would convert the above `^` into start-of-line instead of start-of-input, see: https://stackoverflow.com/a/6143347/2518889.
